{"tid":48230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"晴報：Annual Dinner逼員工倒貼$500買禮物","createTime":"2016-12-21T02:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T12:42:29.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33e244b3b0ba33bba8509c04e0edcc86878c5a13","tid":48230,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;有網民指，過去公司交換禮物只要求買50元的禮物，今年人事部卻要求提升至500元，又提出禮物要體貼同事需要。<br />\n<br />\n帖文指，「今年交換禮物主題係要關心同事，唔可以送杯、相框呢啲行貨或者惡搞&hellip;&hellip;最有心思嗰3個，老闆會每人畀返3千蚊。」<br />\n<br />\n活動形式化 員工或感負面<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛向事主獻計，有人笑說送「一張內有400蚊儲值的八達通卡，夠晒體貼同事需要」。另有網民呻同事發起交換禮物也要列出清單，說明哪些禮物不能買，不滿連選購的自由也沒有。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n環球管理諮詢有限公司董事總經理李漢祥指，<span style=\"color: red;\">具規模的公司舉辦Annual Dinner多數會邀請商業拍檔贊助禮物，罕有叫員工夾錢或自資交換禮物。</span>"},{"pid":"1688fd4cc7f56c79ee61cfc77806f24f0452facc","tid":48230,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:52:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998dd2463108c7c32f108dbc36d56ff90ecec770","tid":48230,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"禮物自備仲要限呢樣限嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9e7638d05148f824ecf9363d9ff504ec6cdd5c","tid":48230,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:59:36.000Z","msg":"晴報有無用連登文？"},{"pid":"353c3431d4c9268bd0db6496688c4972d19d21b0","tid":48230,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"女同事會否將自己標價500蚊1Q代替禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db13c798d1d5df2bc7aa2e7097b619bbc9957342","tid":48230,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女同事會否將自己標價500蚊1Q代替禮物&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif&quot; class=&quot;h